modName: Winterhold Abandoned House On The Edge
summary: This plugin adds a Abandoned House in the Winterhold town on the edge of falling down the mountain because of the event that occurred sometime ago. You will get the impression inside the house that it\'s on the edge of a cliff. Kinda :)
descriptionHtml:
This plugin adds a Abandoned House in the Winterhold town on the edge of falling down the mountain because of the event that occurred sometime ago. You will get the impression inside the house that it\'s on the edge of a cliff. Kinda :)

Perhaps it was no luck that this specific house at the edge of the world stands left? Barely ..


v0.2 
- Adds an old tree that has fallen on the house.
- Adds some adjustments to the landscape underneath the house and close around to make it look better.
- Adds a bed, dresser, chair and barrels and some other minor stuff.
- Fixed a minor bug.

v0.1
- Adds Abandoned House in Winterhold and some trees and shrubs around it.

If this is something people like, I\'ll continue to work on it..
Any feedback, both negative and positive is welcoming in the comment section.
author: Jacob1724
